here it is the directory layout of the AI - delelopment

/ai-proctoring-service
│
├── /models
│   ├── face_detection.py         # Detect multiple faces, spoofing, etc.
│   ├── audio_analysis.py         # Detect background voices, noise anomalies
│   └── behavior_monitor.py       # Optional: gaze tracking, head movement
│
├── /utils
│   ├── video_stream_handler.py   # Frame extraction, preprocessing
│   ├── audio_stream_handler.py   # Audio segmentation, feature extraction
│   └── logger.py                 # Logging and alert generation
│
├── /api
│   ├── routes.py                 # Flask/FastAPI endpoints
│   └── middleware.py             # Auth, rate limiting, etc.
│
├── /config
│   └── settings.yaml             # Thresholds, model paths, tuning params
│
├── /tests
│   ├── test_face_detection.py
│   ├── test_audio_analysis.py
│   └── test_api_endpoints.py
│
├── requirements.txt             # Python dependencies
├── run.py                       # Entry point for the service
└── README.md
